											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="~The player walks up the to the misty ruins of a fort, all that remains is a stone outline of where the structure once stood. A single corner has survived mostly intact, providing shelter and privacy.&#xD;&#xA;~Laezel waits inside the stone parameter of some ruins as the player approaches, when they get close enough to see where she's headed, she guides them to walks over to the doorway of an old guard house&#xD;&#xA;~She walks to the doorway facing the inside, it's pitch black, save a few shafts of light breaking between the slats of a wooden roof. She turns to face the player, arms on the doorway, placing a hand on the door frame" />
